The semantics of NoBuffer, is described in the extensions of both InputPinActivation and OutputPinActivation.
Their sendOffers operations is redefined so that remaining tokens are removed if the NoBuffer stereotype is applied.
The same extension is done for ActivityParameterNodeActivation but will be effective only for Input parameter
nodes.
